text: Kizan () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Tatarobashmakovsky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 92 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km south-east from Nachalovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Kizan, Astrakhan Oblast
